events.name: Louisville Cardinals at Wake Forest Demon Deacons

headlines.description: Lamar Jackson threw two touchdown passes and Louisville forced five turnovers in the second half in a 20-19 victory over Wake Forest on Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Louisville forces 5 turnovers in 20-19 win over Wake

events.name: East Carolina Pirates at Connecticut Huskies

headlines.description: Arkeel Newsome had a 90-yard touchdown run in the third quarter to help break open a close game and UConn beat East Carolina 31-13 on Friday night.

video.headline: Newsome's big game powers UConn by ECU

headlines.shortLinkText: Newsome runs for 179 yards, leads UConn over ECU 31-13

events.name: Louisiana Tech Bulldogs at Rice Owls

headlines.description: Jeff Driskel threw for 320 yards and four touchdowns, Kenneth Dixon ran for two scores, and Louisiana Tech scored 28 straight in a 42-17 victory over Rice on Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Louisiana Tech scores 28 straight in 42-17 win over Rice

events.name: Wyoming Cowboys at Utah State Aggies

headlines.description: Devante Mays rushed for a career-high 176 yards and two touchdowns, Kent Myers had four scores, and Utah State beat Wyoming 58-27 on Friday night for its 13th straight victory at home.
headlines.shortLinkText: Utah State rolls Wyoming 58-27 for 13th straight home win
